'''神秘果蛋白'''（英语：{{lang|en|Miraculin}}）是一种从[[神秘果|神秘果]]中提取出来的[[糖蛋白|糖蛋白]]，又称作'''奇果蛋白'''及'''神秘果素'''。该[[蛋白|蛋白]]本身并没有[[甜|甜]]味，但能让人在品尝原本不甜的[[酸|酸]]性食物时尝出甜味。这种特性属于一种[[味觉修改|味觉修改]]功能，并非改变了食品本身的化学成分。

== 来源 ==
[[File:Starr_980529-4175_Synsepalum_dulcificum.jpg|thumb]]
{{seealso|神秘果}}
[[神秘果|神秘果树]]是原产于[[西非|西非]]的[[灌木|灌木]]，[[拉丁文|拉丁文]]学名为''Synsepalum dulcificum''或者''Richadella dulcifica''<ref name="jbc-263-23-11536">{{cite journal | author = Theerasilp S, Kurihara Y | title = Complete purification and characterization of the taste-modifying protein, miraculin, from miracle fruit | journal = J. Biol. Chem. | volume = 263 | issue = 23 | pages = 11536–9 | pmid = 3403544 | doi =  | url = http://www.jbc.org/cgi/reprint/263/23/11536 | issn =  | date = August 1988 | access-date = 2009-10-22 | archive-date = 2005-08-27 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20050827005706/http://www.jbc.org/cgi/reprint/263/23/11536 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。这种植物在当地的名称包括taami、asaa以及ledidi。

神秘果蛋白本身不是[[甜|甜]]的，但如果其接触到人类的[[舌头|舌头]]之后，在大约一小时之内再尝[[酸|酸]]的食品如[[柑橘|柑橘]]，就会尝出[[甜|甜]]味。在西非，含有该蛋白的神秘果树的红色小果被用来改善酸性食品的[[口感|口感]]。由于[[神秘果|神秘果]]本身并没有任何特别的[[味道|味道]]，因此其[[:category:味觉修改|味觉修改]]的功能被认为是神奇的，神秘果树也因此得名。

== 发现历史 ==
在神秘果中导致这一现象的活性物质，是由[[日本|日本]]科学家[[栗原坚三|栗原坚三]]教授分离出来的（''Kurihara Kenzō''）<ref name="Ui_1999">{{cite journal | last = Ui | first = Michio | date = 1999 | title = 「薬学会賞受賞栗原堅三氏の業績 : それは「奇蹟の果物」からはじまった | journal = Farumashia | publisher = The Pharmaceutical Society of Japan | volume = 35 | issue = 4 | pages = 365 | url = http://ci.nii.ac.jp/naid/110003660406/en/ | language = ja | trans_title = Kurihara Kenzou Performance Award Pharmaceutical Society said: it is a "miracle fruit" | access-date = 2009-10-22 | archive-date = 2012-04-01 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20120401144753/http://ci.nii.ac.jp/naid/110003660406/en/ | dead-url = no }}</ref> 。他于1968年在《[[科学杂志|科学杂志]]》上发表了这一成果，并在其中将这一新发现的[[化合物|化合物]]根据神秘果树的俗称“Miracle tree”命名为神秘果蛋白（Miraculin）<ref name="pmid5673432">{{cite journal | author = Kurihara K, Beidler LM | title = Taste-modifying protein from miracle fruit | journal = Science (journal) | volume = 161 | issue = 847 | pages = 1241–3 | pmid = 5673432 | doi = 10.1126/science.161.3847.1241 | url = | issn = |date=September 1968}}</ref>。

== 糖蛋白结构 ==
1989年，人们首次成功的对神秘果蛋白进行了[[测序|测序]]，并发现这是一种由191个[[氨基酸|氨基酸]]以及一些[[糖类|糖]]链组成的糖蛋白<ref name="pmid2708331">{{cite journal | author = Theerasilp S, Hitotsuya H, Nakajo S, Nakaya K, Nakamura Y, Kurihara Y | title = Complete amino acid sequence and structure characterization of the taste-modifying protein, miraculin | journal = J. Biol. Chem. | volume = 264 | issue = 12 | pages = 6655–9 | pmid = 2708331 | doi =  | url = http://www.jbc.org/cgi/reprint/264/12/6655 | issn =  | date = April 1989 | access-date = 2009-10-22 | archive-date = 2020-06-09 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200609123612/https://www.jbc.org/content/264/12/6655.full.pdf+html | dead-url = no }}</ref>。它以[[四聚体|四聚体]]的形式呈现，其中的单体两两结成[[二聚体|二聚体]]，而两个[[二聚体|二聚体]]则通过[[二硫键|二硫键]][[聚合|聚合]]成四聚体<ref name="crfsn-32-231">{{cite journal | author = Kurihara Y | title = Characteristics of antisweet substances, sweet proteins, and sweetness-inducing proteins | journal = Crit Rev Food Sci Nutr | volume = 32 | issue = 3 | pages = 231–52 | year = 1992 | pmid = 1418601 | doi = | url = | issn = }}</ref>。

